those two meanings.

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:37.878
The first is a very broad
understanding of capital.

00:02:37.878 --> 00:02:42.404
The second is very close to the
way you would have to think

00:02:42.404 --> 00:02:46.848
about capital in connection with
an economic system called

00:02:46.848 --> 00:02:48.020
capitalism.
 

00:02:48.020 --> 00:02:51.492
So, let's start with the
broader usage,

00:02:51.492 --> 00:02:56.245
"Capital is accumulated
wealth used as a fund in

00:02:56.245 --> 00:02:59.810
