highly mechanized capital

00:13:06.097 --> 00:13:09.009
intensive story.
 

00:13:09.009 --> 00:13:16.139
In the history of the world in
the last thousand years is

00:13:16.139 --> 00:13:23.269
essentially the history of
substitution of the right hand

00:13:23.269 --> 00:13:29.173
